document.full_text: rookie rubby de la rosa enjoyed a successful first major league start in leading the los angeles dodgers to a 6-2 win over the philadelphia phillies and their slumping pitcher roy oswalt on tuesday.
document.title: rookie de la rosa leads dodgers past phillies
